query:
INSERT INTO
    trips (
    trip_assembler_id,fiskeridir_vessel_id,landing_coverage,period,start_precision_id,end_precision_id,start_precision_direction,end_precision_direction,trip_precision_status_id,period_precision,distance,distancer_id,start_port_id,end_port_id,position_layers_status
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::INT[],$2::BIGINT[],$3::tstzrange[],$4::tstzrange[],$5::INT[],$6::INT[],$7::TEXT[],$8::TEXT[],$9::TEXT[],$10::tstzrange[],$11::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$12::INT[],$13::TEXT[],$14::TEXT[],$15::INT[]
    )
         RETURNING trip_id AS "trip_id!:TripId",period AS "period!",landing_coverage AS "landing_coverage!",fiskeridir_vessel_id AS "fiskeridir_vessel_id!"
